Get 45% off the Magic Mind bundle with with my link: [https://magicmind.com/CBOOKJAN](https://magicmind.com/CBOOKJAN)  In this episode of The Major Issues Podcast, the hosts dive into the highly anticipated Creature Commandos, the first animated series in James Gunn’s new DCU. Join us as we break down the first season, examining the wild and eccentric characters that make up this unique team of misfits, as well as how it sets the tone for the future of the DC Universe. From the fascinating world-building to the unexpected blend of humor, action, and heart, we discuss what worked, what could have been better, and what we’re most excited for next. Whether you're a lifelong DC fan or just starting to explore this new era, we’ve got you covered on everything you need to know about Creature Commandos and its place in the DCU's bold new direction!

